## Custom Animation

Control animation duration and GSAP easing via `duration` and `ease`.

### Custom Ease
:::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="BaseAnchorCustomEaseDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <script setup lang="ts">
  import { ref } from 'vue'

  const open = ref(false)
  </script>

  <template>
    <TxBaseAnchor
      v-model="open"
      placement="bottom-start"
      :duration="600"
      ease="elastic.out(1, 0.4)"
    >
      <template #reference>
        <TxButton>Elastic</TxButton>
      </template>

      <div style="width: 240px; padding: 4px;">
        Elastic easing with 600ms duration.
      </div>
    </TxBaseAnchor>
  </template>
---
:::

